{"id": "pos041", "name": "Cam_Charity_687_05_13", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Charity"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Grandma Feng, we're here!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "Ah, \"Furuhata Charity Foundation\", they've gotten a new sign too...\nHow many years have it been, Kaori-chan?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Four, five, six... six years! I wonder if everyone still recognizes me?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "Time sure flies. Kaori-chan was just three years old back then... One blink of the eye and you're all grown-up now. \nWhat do you think of the past few years you spent with this old grandma? Are you happy?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "I'm very happy! Thank you so much for adopting me, grandma Feng! You even let me help with the flower shop! I love seeing the customers' smiling faces!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "Haha... good girl. Here, let's go inside.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Wow, it smells so nice~\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "Because it happens to be lunch time, Kaori-chan!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Aunt Saku! Headmaster Tsumugi too! Long time no see!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "Long time no see. We'll be in your care today too, Mrs. Tsumugi.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "Not at all, we're the ones in your care, Mrs. Huang! You've taken great care of Kaori-chan for the past few years. When we heard that you plan to adopt another child, we were all very delighted.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "I'm flattered. These days, I often hear customers talk about this foundation. They all said that you guys helped everyone a lot... Unlike me, who is already too old to do anything.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "Don't say that, Mrs. Huang. You often gift us flowers for free. We are all very thankful of you.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "Saku has a point. There aren't many good people like you out there. You deserve all the praise you get.\nSetting that aside, why did you want to adopt a child again all of a sudden?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "My back's been hurting real bad lately. The labor at the flower shop is getting more and more difficult for me. An extra person would definitely make things easier... Besides, I want to find Kaori-chan a friend too.\nAh, right. Is your husband not here?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "Same as always. Not taking one step outside his research room...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Little Boy A"], "content": "Big brother, give me one!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Little Boy B"], "content": "Me too! Me too!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "Ah... wait a sec...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Little Boy C"], "content": "Why did you give it to her first! Do you like her more than me!?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "P, please wait... I'll be right there...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">STOP~!!</font>\nEveryone, no rushing!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "Utensils clinging"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Alright, alright. Everybody, line up here. If you haven't wash your hands, go wash them first! Only the good kids who follow the rules will get lunch!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Little Boy A"], "content": "... Big sister, who are you?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Good question. I'm a sorcerer who happens to pass by. Any dish touched by me will become super delicious. Here, this one is for you!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Little Boy A"], "content": "Wow! Thank you, big sister!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Hey, quick, fill up the next bowl. There's still a lot of people waiting behind them.</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Ah, okay...</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "Utensils clinging"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "This one is for you.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Little Boy B"], "content": "It smells so good~ Thank you, big brother!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "... Haha.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Hey, you look good with a smile~ When did you come here?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "R, recently...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "No wonder I've never seen you before. I used to lived here as well, but grandma Feng adopted me and took me away a long time ago.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "Grandma... Feng?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "She is the most awesome and kindest grandma in the entire world. Look, she's right there talking to the headmaster.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "Oh...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "Ah, right. My name is Kaori. What's your name?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "I... I'm...\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "... Will this child... be willing to come with me?\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "Rest assured, Mrs. Huang... Hayato is a good kid. He'll be more than happy to go with you.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Charity"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "ホウおばあちゃん！着いたよ！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "あらあら、「古畑慈善機構」なんて看板がかかっているよ。\nもう何年になるかねぇ。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "4、5、6……6年！\nまだみんな私のこと覚えてるかな？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "時間が経つのは早いねぇ……\nあの時まだ薫は3歳だったのに。\nもうこんなに大きくなって。\nおばあちゃんとの生活はどうだい？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "楽しいよ！\nホウおばあちゃん、私を引き取ってくれてありがとう。\nそれに、花屋で働かせてもらって。\n私、お客さんの笑顔が大好き！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "ははは……いい子だね。\nおいで、中に入ろう。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "ドアを開ける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "わぁ～いい匂い！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "ちょうどご飯の時間だからね。\n薫ちゃん！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "咲（サク）おばちゃん！それに紬（ツムギ）院長も！\n久しぶり！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "久しぶりだねぇ。\n今日はよろしくね、紬さん。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "コウさん、こちらこそ、よろしくお願いしますね！\nこの数年薫に良くしていただいて……その上、もう一人子供を引き取りたいだなんて。\n本当にありがとうございます！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "いやいや、とんでもないよ。\nお客さんからもよくここの話は聞いてるよ。\nあなたたちに助けられてるって……\n私のようなばばぁには何もできることはないよ。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "そんなことありませんよ。\nコウさんには、よくお花を送っていただいて……みんな感謝しています。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "咲の言う通りですよ。\nあなたのような方は多くありません。\nでも、なぜまた急にもう一人引き取りたいだなんて？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "最近背中が痛くてねぇ。\n花屋の仕事がしんどいのさ。\nもう一人手伝ってくれる子が増えれば、助かるだろうと思ってね……\nそれに、薫にも友達がいた方がいいだろう？\nそういえば、旦那さんはどうしたんだい？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "いつも通りですよ。\nまた研究室にこもってます……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["男の子 A"], "content": "兄ちゃん！もう1杯！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["女の子 B"], "content": "私も！私も！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "あぁ……ちょっと待ってね……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["男の子 C"], "content": "なんであいつが先なんだよ！\n兄ちゃん贔屓すんなよ！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "ま、待ってって……すぐだから……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">ストーップ！！</font>\nみんなそんなに慌てないの！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "皿がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "はいはい！みんな並んで！\nまだ手を洗ってない子は、先に手を洗ってくること！\nルールを守れるいい子だけがご飯食べられます！\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["男の子 A"], "content": "……お姉ちゃん、だれ？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "あら、いい質問ね。\n私は通りすがりの魔法使い。\n私が触った料理はぜーんぶ超おいしくなっちゃうんだから。\nはい！これは君の！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["男の子 A"], "content": "わぁ！ありがとう！お姉ちゃん！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">ちょっと、早く次のごはんよそって。\nまだまだ人いるんだから。</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">あ、うん……</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "皿がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "はい、どうぞ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["女の子 B"], "content": "いい匂い～\nお兄ちゃんありがとう！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "……はは。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "笑った方がいいじゃん！\nあなた、いつからここにいるの？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "さ、最近……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "だから見覚えないのか～\n私もね、ここに住んでたんだ。\nでも、今はホウおばあちゃんに引き取られて、一緒に暮らしてるの。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "ホウ……おばあちゃん？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "この世で一番優しくて、最高なおばあちゃん。\nほら、あそこで院長と話してる。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "あぁ……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "そうだ、私薫。\nあなたの名前は？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "僕……僕は……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "……この子は……うちに来てくれるかしらねぇ……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "大丈夫ですよ。\n隼人（ハヤト）はいい子です。\nきっと喜びますよ。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Charity"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "芳奶奶，我們到了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "啊，「古畑慈善機構」，連招牌都掛上了……過幾年了啊，小薰？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "四、五、六……六年了！不知道大家還認不認得我？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "日子過得真快，那時候小薰才三歲……一眨眼就長這麼大了。這幾年陪著奶奶還開心吧？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "開心！謝謝芳奶奶把我接出來，還讓我在花店幫忙！我最喜歡客人的笑臉了！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "哈哈……好女孩。來，我們進去吧。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "哇，好香的味道～\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "因為剛好是吃飯時間啊，小薰！\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "咲阿姨！還有紬院長！好久不見！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "好久不見啊。今天也要麻煩了，紬小姐。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "我們才麻煩您呢，黃太太！您這幾年把小薰照顧得好好的，聽到您想多領養一位小朋友，我們大家都很高興呢。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "哪兒的話，最近常聽客人聊到這機構，都說妳們幫了大家不少……哪像我一把老骨頭什麼也做不了。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "才不會呢，黃太太常常送花給我們，我們大家都很感謝您的。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "咲說的沒錯，像您這樣的人可不多呢。不過，怎麼突然又動了領養的念頭啊？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "最近背好痛，花店的活兒越來越吃不消囉，多一個人總是比較輕鬆……也能幫小薰找個朋友。對了，你先生不在嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "老樣子，還悶在研究室呢，他……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小男孩 A"], "content": "哥哥，給我一碗！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小女孩 B"], "content": "我也要！我也要！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "啊……等等……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小男孩 C"], "content": "為什麼先給她！哥哥偏心！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "等、等一下……馬上就好……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">停～！！</font>\n大家都不要急！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "碗盤碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "好了好了，大家排好隊，還沒洗手的去洗完手再過來！守規矩的小朋友才有午餐吃唷。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小男孩 A"], "content": "……姐姐，妳是誰啊？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "問得好，我是路過的魔法師，被我碰過的料理都會變得超級美味喔。來，這碗是你的！\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小男孩 A"], "content": "哇！謝謝姐姐！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">喂，快裝下一碗呀，後面還有好多人耶。</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊，好……</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "碗盤碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "這碗給妳。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["小女孩 B"], "content": "好香喔～謝謝哥哥！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "……哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "笑起來很棒嘛～你是什麼時候來這裡的啊？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "最、最近……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "難怪我沒見過你。我也住過這裡喔，不過好久以前就被芳奶奶接走了。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "芳……奶奶？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "是全世界最棒、最溫柔的奶奶。你看，她正在跟院長說話呢。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "喔……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "對了，我叫做薰，你叫什麼名字啊？\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "我……我是……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "……不知道這孩子……願不願意呢？\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "放心，黃太太……隼人是個好孩子，他一定會很高興的。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Charity"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "팡 할머니! 우리 왔어!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "아, 「후루하타 자선 기구」라... 이제 간판도 생겼구나... 몇 년이나 흘렀지, Kaori?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "4, 5, 6......6년! 다들 날 알아볼까?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "세월 참 빠르구나. 그때 Kaori는 3살이었는데... 순식간에 이렇게 커버렸어. 몇 년 동안 이 할미랑 같이 지내서 즐거웠니?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "물론이지! 날 받아줘서, 그리고 꽃집에서 지낼 수 있게 해줘서 너무 고마워 할머니. 난 손님들의 미소를 보는 게 제일 좋아!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "하하하... 우리 아가, 참 착하기도 하지... 자, 들어가자구나.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_School", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "와, 엄청 향기로운 냄새~\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "이제 막 밥 먹을 시간이라서 그렇단다, Kaori!\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "사쿠 이모! 츠무기 원장님! 오랜만이에요!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "오랜만입니다. 오늘도 잘 부탁드리겠습니다, 츠무기 씨.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "황 부인, 저희야말로 잘 부탁드려요! 몇 년 동안 Kaori를 이렇게나 잘 돌봐주셨는걸요. 한 명을 더 입양하고 싶다고 하셨을 때, 저희 모두 얼마나 기뻤는지 모릅니다.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "과찬이세요. 최근 손님들이 이 기구에 대해 이야기하는 걸 들었어요. 이곳에서 많은 도움을 받았었다고... 그에 비하면 저 같은 늙은이는 한 게 아무것도 없답니다.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Saku"], "content": "그런 말씀 마세요. 황 부인도 자주 이곳에 꽃을 보내주셨잖아요. 정말 너무나 감사드려요.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "Saku 말이 맞습니다. 당신 같은 분은 흔치 않아요. 그런데 어떻게 또 한 명을 더 입양할 생각을?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "최근에 등이 아파오기 시작하더군요. 이대로면 꽃가게를 운영하는 데도 무리가... 한 명이 더 있으면 조금 나아질 것 같기도 하고 우리 Kaori가 새로운 친구도 사귈 수 있고 해서... 참, 남편분은?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "늘 그랬듯이 계속 연구실에 있죠. 그이는...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["남자 아이 A"], "content": "형! 한 그릇 더!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["여자 아이 B"], "content": "나도! 나도!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "아... 잠깐만...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["남자 아이 C"], "content": "왜 쟤 먼저 주는 거야? \n흥! 왜 편애해?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "자, 잠깐만... 금방...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">스톱!!!</font>\n다들 뭐가 그리 급한 거야!?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "접시가 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "좋아 좋아~ 자, 제대로 줄 서시고요~ 아직 손 안 씻은 사람들은 손부터 씻고 오세요! 말 잘 듣는 사람한테만 맛~있는 거 줄 거니까!\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["남자 아이 A"], "content": "...누나는 누구야?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "좋은 질문이야! 사실... 나는 이 근방을 지나가던 마법사야. 내가 건드리는 음식은 모두 엄청 맛있게 변하거든~ 자, 이건 네 거!\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["남자 아이 A"], "content": "와! 고마워 누나!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">야. 빨리 그릇 채워. 뒤에 줄 엄청 서있잖아.</font>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">아, 알았어...</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Dishes", "접시가 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "이건 네 거.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["여자 아이 B"], "content": "우와아! 냄새 진짜 좋다!\n고마워 형!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "...하하하.\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "image", "attrs": ["pos4101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "웃으니까 훨씬 보기 좋잖아~ \n넌 언제 여기로 온 거야?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "아, 최... 최근에...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "어쩐지 한 번도 본 적이 없는 얼굴이라더니. 나도 이곳에 살았었어. 엄청 옛날에 팡 할머니가 데려가 주시긴 했지만.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "팡... 할머니?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "세상에서 가장 멋지고 가장 따뜻한 할머니야! 저기, 지금 원장님이랑 이야기하고 있는 사람 보이지?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "아아...\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "아, 난 Kaori라고 해.\n넌?\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "나... 나는...\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "...이 아이가 원할지 안 원할지 모르겠네요.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Tsumugi"], "content": "걱정 마세요, 황 부인... Hayato는 정말 좋은 아이에요. 그리고 분명 엄청 기뻐할 겁니다.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Charity"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "芳奶奶，我們到了！\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "啊，「古畑慈善機構」，連招牌都掛上了……過幾年了啊，小薰？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "四、五、六……六年了！不知道大家還認不認得我？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "日子過得真快，那時候小薰才三歲……一眨眼就長這麼大了。這幾年陪著奶奶還開心吧？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kaori"], "content": "開心！謝謝芳奶奶把我接出來，還讓我在花店幫忙！我最喜歡客人的笑臉了！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Feng"], "content": "哈哈…